Package cscie97.asn4.ecommerce.exception

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CollectionNotFoundException
    Exception for problems that the CollectionImporter may run into during typical operation.
    ContentNotFoundException
    Exception for problems that the CollectionImporter, ContentImporter, or SearchEngine may run into during typical operation.
    ImportException
    Exception for problems that the Importer and SearchEngine may run into during typical operation.
    MobileAppException
    Exception for problems that might occur in any of the cscie97.asn4.ecommerce.collection, cscie97.asn4.ecommerce.product, or cscie97.asn4.ecommerce.csv classes.
    ParseException
    Exception for problems that the Importer or SearchEngine may run into during typical operation such as importing Countries, Devices, Content, or executing queries.
    QueryEngineException
    Exception for problems that the SearchEngine may run into during typical query execution.
